{"tid":2175931,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"晴空物語 有無人回鍋玩返？","createTime":"2020-08-26T19:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T04:25:56.000Z","uid":208766,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69dbdaabf1d8f16a56e26be94695455719c281ff","tid":2175931,"uid":208766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUX6qTB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUX6qTB.png&h=21a784ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪無咩人記得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得係玩過最好玩嘅online game<br />\n竟然可以download仲要登入到，有冇人已經玩緊？<br />\n當時執笠覺得好可惜，唔知幾耐又冇私服，一直都好想玩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打金裝 擲骰公平分裝 合寵合武合符文<br />\n寵物仲要捉寵 捉完合寵 唔靚技就洗到啱技為止 難到仆街<br />\n星光銀幣 抽騎抽時裝 覺得佢啲時裝好靚<br />\nPVP 鳳狙一箭收皮 <br />\n熱門時期 分身開隻塔皇掛十字位 可以收金帶人升lv(200金 一位一個鐘)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有晴空塔/打會戰個啲好似⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">細個仲會識mon，扮熄咗電腦，走去日掛夜掛EXP/WP波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n已經好多唔記得，有冇人回憶返，一齊回味下，諗返依家啲game完全搵唔番呢啲樂趣，剩係得個錢字就會勁。"},{"pid":"d8cf4388a7b3a7d2baa09e499aeafd7d6411826a","tid":2175931,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T19:08:14.000Z","msg":"記得"},{"pid":"9104f6edea0ce47bcdae011d979ff8da01b4f6c1","tid":2175931,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T19:09:18.000Z","msg":"但執得一次會執第二次都唔奇"},{"pid":"15df71b31f8172b3ae1eb70170e74276be5e26e7","tid":2175931,"uid":208766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T19:11:27.000Z","msg":"另外之前公會係入咗「最後的旗幟」。"},{"pid":"d22dc78e5b849f6f8e3005e3e8091be0c8f98192","tid":2175931,"uid":95777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"好懷念"},{"pid":"f4244d6c40a80cde97c1718521a2ca4c2c85037f","tid":2175931,"uid":145012,"lik